{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "仁之事者，必務求興天下之利，除天下之害。", "text_normalized": "仁之事者，必務求興天下之利，除天下之害。", "canonical_ref": "26.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "將以為法乎天下，利人乎即為，不利人乎即止。", "text_normalized": "將以為法乎天下，利人乎即為，不利人乎即止。", "canonical_ref": "26.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "且夫仁者之為天下度也，非為其目之所美，耳之所樂，口之所甘，身體之所安，以此虧奪民衣食之財，仁者弗為也。", "text_normalized": "且夫仁者之為天下度也，非為其目之所美，耳之所樂，口之所甘，身體之所安，以此虧奪民衣食之財，仁者弗為也。", "canonical_ref": "26.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "是故子墨子之所以非樂者，非以大鐘鳴鼓、琴瑟竽笙之聲以為不樂也，非以刻鏤華文章之色以為不美也，非以犓豢煎炙之味以為不甘也，非以高台厚榭邃野之居以為不安也。", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子之所以非樂者，非以大鐘鳴鼓、琴瑟竽笙之聲以為不樂也，非以刻鏤華文章之色以為不美也，非以犓豢煎炙之味以為不甘也，非以高台厚榭邃野之居以為不安也。", "canonical_ref": "26.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "雖身知其安也，口知其甘也，目知其美也，耳知其樂也，然上考之不中聖王之事，下度之不中萬民之利。", "text_normalized": "雖身知其安也，口知其甘也，目知其美也，耳知其樂也，然上考之不中聖王之事，下度之不中萬民之利。", "canonical_ref": "26.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "為樂非也。", "text_normalized": "為樂非也。", "canonical_ref": "26.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "今王公大人雖無造為樂器，以為事乎國家，非直掊潦水、拆壤垣而為之也，將必厚措斂乎萬民，以為大鐘鳴鼓、琴瑟竽笙之聲。", "text_normalized": "今王公大人雖無造為樂器，以為事乎國家，非直掊潦水、拆壤垣而為之也，將必厚措斂乎萬民，以為大鐘鳴鼓、琴瑟竽笙之聲。", "canonical_ref": "26.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "古者聖王，亦嘗厚措斂乎萬民，以為舟車。", "text_normalized": "古者聖王，亦嘗厚措斂乎萬民，以為舟車。", "canonical_ref": "26.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "既以成矣，曰：", "text_normalized": "既以成矣，曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "「吾將惡許用之？", "text_normalized": "「吾將惡許用之？", "canonical_ref": "26.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "」曰：", "text_normalized": "」曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "「舟用之水，車用之陸，君子息其足焉，小人休其肩背焉。", "text_normalized": "「舟用之水，車用之陸，君子息其足焉，小人休其肩背焉。", "canonical_ref": "26.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "」故萬民出財繼而予之，不敢以為慼恨者，何也？", "text_normalized": "」故萬民出財繼而予之，不敢以為慼恨者，何也？", "canonical_ref": "26.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "以其反中民之利也。", "text_normalized": "以其反中民之利也。", "canonical_ref": "26.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "然則樂器反中民之利，亦若此，即我弗敢非也。", "text_normalized": "然則樂器反中民之利，亦若此，即我弗敢非也。", "canonical_ref": "26.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "然則當用樂器，譬之若聖王之為舟車也，即我弗敢非也。", "text_normalized": "然則當用樂器，譬之若聖王之為舟車也，即我弗敢非也。", "canonical_ref": "26.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "民有三患，饑者不得食，寒者不得衣，勞者不得息，三者民之巨患也。", "text_normalized": "民有三患，饑者不得食，寒者不得衣，勞者不得息，三者民之巨患也。", "canonical_ref": "26.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "然即當為之撞巨鐘、擊鳴鼓、彈琴瑟、吹竽笙而揚干戚，民衣食之財，將安可得乎？", "text_normalized": "然即當為之撞巨鐘、擊鳴鼓、彈琴瑟、吹竽笙而揚干戚，民衣食之財，將安可得乎？", "canonical_ref": "26.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "即我以為未必然也。", "text_normalized": "即我以為未必然也。", "canonical_ref": "26.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "意捨此，今有大國即攻小國，有大家即伐小家，強劫弱，眾暴寡，詐欺愚，貴傲賤，寇亂盜賊並興，不可禁止也。", "text_normalized": "意捨此，今有大國即攻小國，有大家即伐小家，強劫弱，眾暴寡，詐欺愚，貴傲賤，寇亂盜賊並興，不可禁止也。", "canonical_ref": "26.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "然即當為之撞巨鐘、擊鳴鼓、彈琴瑟、吹竽笙而揚干戚，天下之亂也，將安可得而治與？", "text_normalized": "然即當為之撞巨鐘、擊鳴鼓、彈琴瑟、吹竽笙而揚干戚，天下之亂也，將安可得而治與？", "canonical_ref": "26.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "即我未必然也。", "text_normalized": "即我未必然也。", "canonical_ref": "26.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "姑嘗厚措斂乎萬民，以為大鐘鳴鼓、琴瑟竽笙之聲，以求興天下之利，除天下之害，而無補也。", "text_normalized": "姑嘗厚措斂乎萬民，以為大鐘鳴鼓、琴瑟竽笙之聲，以求興天下之利，除天下之害，而無補也。", "canonical_ref": "26.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "為樂非也。", "text_normalized": "為樂非也。", "canonical_ref": "26.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "今王公大人唯毋處高台厚榭之上而視之，鍾猶是延鼎也，弗撞擊將何樂得焉哉！", "text_normalized": "今王公大人唯毋處高台厚榭之上而視之，鍾猶是延鼎也，弗撞擊將何樂得焉哉！", "canonical_ref": "26.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "其說將必撞擊之。", "text_normalized": "其說將必撞擊之。", "canonical_ref": "26.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "惟勿撞擊，將必不使老與遲者。", "text_normalized": "惟勿撞擊，將必不使老與遲者。", "canonical_ref": "26.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "老與遲者，耳目不聰明，股肱不畢強，聲不和調，明不轉樸。", "text_normalized": "老與遲者，耳目不聰明，股肱不畢強，聲不和調，明不轉樸。", "canonical_ref": "26.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "將必使當年，因其耳目之聰明，股肱之畢強，聲之和調，眉之轉樸。", "text_normalized": "將必使當年，因其耳目之聰明，股肱之畢強，聲之和調，眉之轉樸。", "canonical_ref": "26.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "使丈夫為之，廢丈夫耕稼樹蓺之時；", "text_normalized": "使丈夫為之，廢丈夫耕稼樹蓺之時；", "canonical_ref": "26.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "使婦人為之，廢婦人紡績織紝之事。", "text_normalized": "使婦人為之，廢婦人紡績織紝之事。", "canonical_ref": "26.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "今王公大人，唯毋為樂，虧奪民衣食之財以拊樂，如此多也。", "text_normalized": "今王公大人，唯毋為樂，虧奪民衣食之財以拊樂，如此多也。", "canonical_ref": "26.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "為樂非也。", "text_normalized": "為樂非也。", "canonical_ref": "26.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "今大鐘鳴鼓、琴瑟竿笙之聲，既已具矣，大人肅然奏而獨聽之，將何樂得焉哉？", "text_normalized": "今大鐘鳴鼓、琴瑟竿笙之聲，既已具矣，大人肅然奏而獨聽之，將何樂得焉哉？", "canonical_ref": "26.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "其說將必與賤人不與君子，與君子聽之，廢君子聽治；", "text_normalized": "其說將必與賤人不與君子，與君子聽之，廢君子聽治；", "canonical_ref": "26.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "與賤人聽之，廢賤人之從事。", "text_normalized": "與賤人聽之，廢賤人之從事。", "canonical_ref": "26.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "今王公大人惟毋為樂，虧奪民之衣食之財以拊樂，如此多也。", "text_normalized": "今王公大人惟毋為樂，虧奪民之衣食之財以拊樂，如此多也。", "canonical_ref": "26.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "為樂非也。", "text_normalized": "為樂非也。", "canonical_ref": "26.44", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 45, "text_original": "昔者齊康公興樂萬，萬人不可衣短褐，不可食糠糟，曰：", "text_normalized": "昔者齊康公興樂萬，萬人不可衣短褐，不可食糠糟，曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.45", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 46, "text_original": "「食飲不美，面目顏色不足視也；", "text_normalized": "「食飲不美，面目顏色不足視也；", "canonical_ref": "26.46", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 47, "text_original": "衣服不美，身體從容丑羸不足觀也。", "text_normalized": "衣服不美，身體從容丑羸不足觀也。", "canonical_ref": "26.47", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 48, "text_original": "」是以食必粱肉，衣必文繡。", "text_normalized": "」是以食必粱肉，衣必文繡。", "canonical_ref": "26.48", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 49, "text_original": "此掌不從事乎衣食之財，而掌食乎人者也。", "text_normalized": "此掌不從事乎衣食之財，而掌食乎人者也。", "canonical_ref": "26.49", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 50, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.50", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 51, "text_original": "今王公大人，惟毋為樂，虧奪民衣食之財以拊樂，如此之也。", "text_normalized": "今王公大人，惟毋為樂，虧奪民衣食之財以拊樂，如此之也。", "canonical_ref": "26.51", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 52, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.52", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 53, "text_original": "為樂非也。", "text_normalized": "為樂非也。", "canonical_ref": "26.53", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 54, "text_original": "今人固與禽獸、麋鹿、蜚鳥、貞蟲異者也。", "text_normalized": "今人固與禽獸、麋鹿、蜚鳥、貞蟲異者也。", "canonical_ref": "26.54", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 55, "text_original": "今之禽獸、麋鹿、蜚鳥、貞蟲，因其羽毛以為衣裘。", "text_normalized": "今之禽獸、麋鹿、蜚鳥、貞蟲，因其羽毛以為衣裘。", "canonical_ref": "26.55", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 56, "text_original": "因其蹄蚤以為褲屨。", "text_normalized": "因其蹄蚤以為褲屨。", "canonical_ref": "26.56", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 57, "text_original": "因其水草以為飲食。", "text_normalized": "因其水草以為飲食。", "canonical_ref": "26.57", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 58, "text_original": "故唯使雄不耕稼樹蓺，雌亦不紡績織紝，衣食之財固已具矣。", "text_normalized": "故唯使雄不耕稼樹蓺，雌亦不紡績織紝，衣食之財固已具矣。", "canonical_ref": "26.58", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 59, "text_original": "今人與此異者也，賴其力者生，不賴其力者不生君子不強聽治，即刑政亂；", "text_normalized": "今人與此異者也，賴其力者生，不賴其力者不生君子不強聽治，即刑政亂；", "canonical_ref": "26.59", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 60, "text_original": "賤人不強從事，即財用不足。", "text_normalized": "賤人不強從事，即財用不足。", "canonical_ref": "26.60", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 61, "text_original": "今天下之士君子以吾言不然。", "text_normalized": "今天下之士君子以吾言不然。", "canonical_ref": "26.61", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 62, "text_original": "然即姑嘗數天下分事，而觀樂之害。", "text_normalized": "然即姑嘗數天下分事，而觀樂之害。", "canonical_ref": "26.62", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 63, "text_original": "王公大人蚤朝晏退，聽獄治政，此其分事也。", "text_normalized": "王公大人蚤朝晏退，聽獄治政，此其分事也。", "canonical_ref": "26.63", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 64, "text_original": "士君子竭股肱之力，亶其思慮之智，內治官府，外收斂關市、山林、澤梁之利，以實倉廩府庫，此其分事也。", "text_normalized": "士君子竭股肱之力，亶其思慮之智，內治官府，外收斂關市、山林、澤梁之利，以實倉廩府庫，此其分事也。", "canonical_ref": "26.64", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 65, "text_original": "農夫蚤出暮入，耕稼樹蓺，多聚叔粟，此其分事也。", "text_normalized": "農夫蚤出暮入，耕稼樹蓺，多聚叔粟，此其分事也。", "canonical_ref": "26.65", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 66, "text_original": "婦人夙興夜寐，紡績織紝，多治麻絲葛緒、綑布縿，此其分事也。", "text_normalized": "婦人夙興夜寐，紡績織紝，多治麻絲葛緒、綑布縿，此其分事也。", "canonical_ref": "26.66", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 67, "text_original": "今惟毋在乎王公大人說樂而聽之，即必不能蚤朝晏退，聽獄治政，是故國家亂而社稷危矣！", "text_normalized": "今惟毋在乎王公大人說樂而聽之，即必不能蚤朝晏退，聽獄治政，是故國家亂而社稷危矣！", "canonical_ref": "26.67", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 68, "text_original": "今惟毋在乎士君子說樂而聽之，即必不能竭股肱之力，亶其思慮之智，內治官府，外收斂關市、山林、澤梁之利，以實倉廩府庫，是故倉廩府庫不實。", "text_normalized": "今惟毋在乎士君子說樂而聽之，即必不能竭股肱之力，亶其思慮之智，內治官府，外收斂關市、山林、澤梁之利，以實倉廩府庫，是故倉廩府庫不實。", "canonical_ref": "26.68", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 69, "text_original": "今惟毋在乎農夫說樂而聽之，即必不能蚤出暮入，耕稼樹蓺，多聚叔粟，是故叔粟不足。", "text_normalized": "今惟毋在乎農夫說樂而聽之，即必不能蚤出暮入，耕稼樹蓺，多聚叔粟，是故叔粟不足。", "canonical_ref": "26.69", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 70, "text_original": "今惟毋在乎婦人說樂而聽之，即不必能夙興夜寐，紡績織紝，多治麻絲葛緒、綑布縿，是故佈縿不興。", "text_normalized": "今惟毋在乎婦人說樂而聽之，即不必能夙興夜寐，紡績織紝，多治麻絲葛緒、綑布縿，是故佈縿不興。", "canonical_ref": "26.70", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 71, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.71", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 72, "text_original": "孰為大人之聽治、而廢國家之從事？", "text_normalized": "孰為大人之聽治、而廢國家之從事？", "canonical_ref": "26.72", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 73, "text_original": "曰樂也。", "text_normalized": "曰樂也。", "canonical_ref": "26.73", "notes": ""}
