{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0080", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 80, "text_original": "「其恆舞於宮，是謂巫風。", "text_normalized": "「其恆舞於宮，是謂巫風。", "canonical_ref": "26.80", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0081", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 81, "text_original": "其刑，君子出絲二衛，小人否，似二伯黃徑。", "text_normalized": "其刑，君子出絲二衛，小人否，似二伯黃徑。", "canonical_ref": "26.81", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0082", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 82, "text_original": "」乃言曰：", "text_normalized": "」乃言曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.82", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0083", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 83, "text_original": "「嗚乎！", "text_normalized": "「嗚乎！", "canonical_ref": "26.83", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0084", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 84, "text_original": "舞佯佯，黃言孔章，上帝弗常，九有以亡。", "text_normalized": "舞佯佯，黃言孔章，上帝弗常，九有以亡。", "canonical_ref": "26.84", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0085", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 85, "text_original": "上帝不順，降之百，其家必壞喪。", "text_normalized": "上帝不順，降之百，其家必壞喪。", "canonical_ref": "26.85", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0086", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 86, "text_original": "」察九有之所以亡者，徒從飾樂也。", "text_normalized": "」察九有之所以亡者，徒從飾樂也。", "canonical_ref": "26.86", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0087", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 87, "text_original": "於《武觀》曰：", "text_normalized": "於《武觀》曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.87", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0088", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 88, "text_original": "「啟乃淫溢康樂，野於飲食，將將銘，莧磬以力。", "text_normalized": "「啟乃淫溢康樂，野於飲食，將將銘，莧磬以力。", "canonical_ref": "26.88", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0089", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 89, "text_original": "湛濁於酒，渝食於野，萬舞翼翼，章聞於天，天用弗式。", "text_normalized": "湛濁於酒，渝食於野，萬舞翼翼，章聞於天，天用弗式。", "canonical_ref": "26.89", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0090", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 90, "text_original": "」故上者天鬼弗式，下者萬民弗利。", "text_normalized": "」故上者天鬼弗式，下者萬民弗利。", "canonical_ref": "26.90", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0091", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 91, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "26.91", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0092", "section_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i", "source_id": "mozi-026-condemnation-of-music-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 92, "text_original": "今天下士君子，請將欲求興天下之利，除天下之害，當在樂之為物，將不可不禁而止也。", "text_normalized": "今天下士君子，請將欲求興天下之利，除天下之害，當在樂之為物，將不可不禁而止也。", "canonical_ref": "26.92", "notes": ""}
